batteries in these items have not been affected from the fire. The =
standard process in this situation is that you can undertake any testing =
of any of your items which you wish to, to obtain test results or a =
report which your insurer can consider for inclusion in your claims. If =
the test results prove any damage or loss to these items from the fire =
=E2=80=93 then your insurer will consider them within your =
